#277
On the Battlements~
Atop the western battlements of Castle Britannia, you have a marvellous
view of the royal orchards below.  Their fragrant blossoms waft up to your
nose, bringing the pleasant smell of fruit.  The orchards grow all manner of
fruit and nut, but are renowned for thier apples, the likes of which have
not been seen this side of New Magicina.  The battlements extend into the
distance to the north, and lead into the southwest guard tower to the south.
To the east, a short staircase leads to the flat rooftop of the castle.  
