Storage Room~
This is a storage room.  Typically enough, many things are stored here. 
For the most part, the room is filled with foodstuffs.  Several large casks
dominate one wall, most likely filled with the finest wine from Empath
Abbey.  The room also has many sacks of grain and flour leaning against
several rows of crates stacked to well above your height.  The other side of
the room is filled with barrels of many types, filled with preserves of
various sorts, and other combestibles.  The only door from the room is to
the east.  
