artifact collected on the Avatar's adventures.  Everything from blackrock to
runestones litter the shelves and chests in this room, giving the room a
generally disused to it.  The equipment appears not to have been disturbed
in many years.  A heavy iron door is to the west, which leads out of the
armory.  
